# Future Slide Skill — landing page
#
# This site is fully static and currently requires NO environment variables
# at runtime. Copy this file to `.env.local` if you ever need to add one.
#
# Vite convention:
#   - Variables MUST be prefixed with VITE_ to be exposed to client code.
#   - Without the prefix, the value is only available at build/config time.
#   - Files are loaded in this order (later overrides earlier):
#       .env  →  .env.local  →  .env.[mode]  →  .env.[mode].local
#   - Never commit real secrets — anything VITE_-prefixed ships to the browser.
#
# Reference: https://vite.dev/guide/env-and-mode

# --- Optional analytics / observability (uncomment when needed) ---
# VITE_PLAUSIBLE_DOMAIN=futureslide.example
# VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# --- Optional public site origin (used in OG/canonical tags if added later) ---
# VITE_SITE_URL=https://futureslide.example
